cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

This paper proposes a novel example weighting framework for training neural networks, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and natural language processing (cs.CL) since the proposed framework can be applied to various datasets and tasks. However, since the experiments mainly focus on image classification tasks, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.CL.
